_:f896e39d103261726fbb52ad94160d3f a <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E52_Time-span> ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> " He was a monk of medieval Ethiopia who was the head of the monastery of Dabra Ṣǝmmunā in\n                  Mugār. According to his Acts he was aggressive in his missionary activity and is said to have flogged a non-Christian priest in public and\n                  burnt the house of the others. He is credited for converting the Beta ʾƎsraʾel into Christianity in\n                  Ṣallamt and Sǝmen. He was a spiritual counsellor \n                  of Queen Žan Kallal and her son King Baʾǝda Māryām I.\n               " .
